rawContent:
Crawling under
And within,
Love is leaving,
Vanishing.
I don't know or 
What went wrong,
All I know is 
Love has gone,
On the days 
I look inside,
Any morsel
I can find,
In the recess
Of the truth,
Love has 
Vanished with
The blues!
